    "For TCGA-BRCA, evidence of association with breast cancer or cancer in general can be found for all the identified pathways in previous literatures (see Supplementary Table 5 for list of references).",
    "The pathway with frequency three in Supplementary Fig. 7a, R-HSA-163560, is triglyceride catabolism.",
